id: pm-kipd
title: "GH-438: accept a full item JSON document on stdin for pm create / pm update"
description: "Dogfood GH-438: no single-document create/update; agents translate items into 10-20 flags. Duplicate check: searched stdin json/document create — only per-field stdin support (--dep -, --note -) exists; no open overlap."
type: Feature
status: open
priority: 2
tags[3]: agent-ux,"area:cli",gh-issue
